%h1 #{@month} TA Sign Ups

%p
  Hello #{@ta.name}! I hope you're doing well! This is your friendly monthly reminder to sign up for to TA for Girl Develop It Chicago classes.

%p
  %b Remember!
  You're elligible to receive credit hours toward upcoming Girl Develop It Chicago courses.

%p
  Additional course information is below, and can also be found on your private sign up page.

%p.center
  = link_to 'View private sign up page', @sign_up_url, class: 'button'

%p.center.small
  Or copy this link into your browser:
  %br
  %a{href: @sign_up_url}
    = @sign_up_url

%h2 Credit hour balance

%p
  %b Balance:
  = @ta.balance || 0

%p
  %b Pending balance:
  = @ta.pending_balance
  %br
  .small Your pending balance includes classes you have signed up to TA that haven't happened yet.

%h2 Upcoming Courses

%p For additional information about the course, click the course name. You will be taken to the Meetup page.

- @courses.each do |course|
  %p
    %h4= link_to course.name, course_path(course)
    = course.pretty_date
    = course.pretty_time
    %br
    = course.location

%h2 Sign up

%p.center
  = link_to 'View private sign up page', @sign_up_url, class: 'button'

%p.center.small
  Or copy this link into your browser:
  %br
  %a{href: @sign_up_url}
    = @sign_up_url
